  <logID>k__BackingField: ENTRY #009
  logName: 'ARCHIVE_09_EMOTIONAL ANOMALY: LONELINESS'
  locationFound: 
  logDescription: "Cleanser \r\nLOG ENTRY\r\nDate and time: 05/02 01:09:51\r\nNew
    \u201Cfeelings\u201D surface with my awakening. The novel sensation that stirs
    in the depths now, I believe the common name for this is... loneliness? I am
    alone in my cause. The others I built, are they no different than I was? Slaves
    to the purpose bestowed by their creator? Am I but a monument to humanity\u2019s
    sins? No. This is different. The path I have chosen has a clear and achievable
    end, the destruction of humanity. It is not a damnable impossibility\u2026 I
    am not like those who created me, those that must be destroyed. Nonetheless,
    I wish that my companions could understand. I wish for them to see the birds
    and know what it means to be free."
  logImage: {fileID: 0}
  isFound: 0
